{"tid":2283171,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［自家烘焙］農夫包","createTime":"2020-11-12T11:15:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T10:22:17.000Z","uid":132749,"like":32,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5ba60a188f3ede88a8a13f6a0890426d3b5a15ed","tid":2283171,"uid":132749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T11:15:12.000Z","msg":"又係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今次用酸種同乾依士整左個農夫包，宜個方法比就咁用酸種易好多。 就咁用酸種好視乎個種養得好唔好。  特別岩岩養好既種，力度唔太夠， 發好耐先發好， 宜個方法慳返唔少時間。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但整出黎都好好食，好有彈性<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次整就無𠝹花，諗住拎黎整其他野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FCanHUx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFCanHUx.png&h=ea57a9f5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E2XUy1e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE2XUy1e.png&h=129ff4b6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jp7xkGf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJp7xkGf.png&h=a079b960&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2E0uuC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2E0uuC.jpg&h=1fa05954&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r04jK29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr04jK29.jpg&h=008db18d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UblgFqvh614\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUblgFqvh614&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2Byh6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=b9fa22b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UblgFqvh614</a><br />\n如果對酸種有興趣既，可以睇返我之前個post <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2252281/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2252281/page/1<